ActEnergy Efficiency Act
PrecisRegulations amending the ENERGY EFFICIENCY REGULATIONS by increasing the stringency of existing minimum energy-perfomance standards (MEPS) for four currently regulated products (e.g., residential gas furnaces) , introduce new MEPS and associated reporting and compliance requirements for six products (e.g., commercial clothes washers), introduce MEPS for general service lamps, and require consumer energy performance labelling for general service lamps and incandescent reflector lamps, and for compact fluorescent lamps.
